name: Pop Art Owl 6
description:
This limited series of owl pop art was created to use in a collaboration project between Oopsy Owl @BudsOwl and MyNash @myknash for the #Blinddate tezos community event February 2022.  

The Original project can be seen at https://teia.art/objkt/669473, a few people were asking were they could collect the owl prints in the project, so we decided to mint them in small editions.
